Guardian Angel by Laffpro

There are forces beyond our perception and understanding, they are powerful, they are loving, and they keep the fair equilibrium in this world. With so much happening with our lovely planet right now, we all need the Guardian Angel.

Soothing uprising soundtrack and colourful animation merged into the unique [1/1] Audio-Visual NFT Artwork minted exclusively at Foundation.

Upon purchase, you will get the HD animated version of the artwork, and the poster still PNG image.
